10k to spend on armor and weapons.  I would like to buy a full suit of some sort of armor, because I like the looks of actually have a full suit of something rather than bits and pieces.  I would also like to purchase 2 half decent weapons.  There is also the age old question of whether I should dual wield or use 2hs, i plan on doing both but will probably dual wield most of the time unless anyone can give me a good argument against it.  <br>
<br>
So basically i have 3 questions...<br>
<br>
1.  Half Elf, Ogre, Troll?  I like them all, i enjoy all of their looks and think each makes a good warrior.  I honestly dont' know if I can choose so please provide some arguments.<br>
2.  What is a good full suit of armor considering my money situation?  Or should I go bits and pieces?<br>
3.  Can you present a good argument to use 2hs over dual wielding?<br>
<br>
Also keep in mind that I'd like to not have 2 great weapons and crappy armor, or great armor and crappy weapons -- I want to be well balanced. <br>
<br>
